<p><strong>P &amp; O Ferries</strong></p>
<p><strong>Dover-Calais</strong></p>
<p>Five Superferries operate a 75-minute crossing. Priority boarding is available at a supplement of £10.50 per car per crossing. Club class which gives you the luxury of the Club Lounge with complimentary tea or coffee and newspapers is available at a supplement of £10.50 per person per crossing.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Hull to Zeebrugge or Rotterdam</strong></p>
<p>Daily overnight service. Accommodation onboard is compulsory and a supplement is charged for this – seats are no longer available following the introduction of the new luxury ships. Meals are not included, but can be pre-booked. Details on request.</p>
