<p><strong>Hire a Car with Holiday Autos</strong></p>
<p>Hire a car and gain the freedom and flexiblity to make the most of your resort and explore your holiday region at your own pace!</p>
<p>Working with partners including Avis, Alamo, Europcar, Sixt, Hertz, National, Thrifty and Budget, Holiday Autos offers competitively priced car hire and a high level of service for all its customers. Cars can be rented at all our arrival airports for the duration of your holiday and also available in some of our major resorts as well enabling you to hire for shorter periods, to explore the local area and perhaps ski further afield.</p>
<p>For more information please click below or call 0871 472 5229 and quote ref xingh1</p>
<p>Booking your car hire is easy just choose the pick-up point, dates and car you require from the selection shown for an instant quote. You can choose the insurance package that is right for you and select any extras such as baby seats, snow chains, etc.</p>
